---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { Container } from '../../components/layout/Container';
import { Section } from '../../components/layout/Section';
import { Heading } from '../../components/ui/Heading';
import { Badge } from '../../components/ui/Badge';
import { Button } from '../../components/ui/Button';
import { Card } from '../../components/ui/Card';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Case Study: Law Firm Generates $2.4M in Cases with $18K Ad Spend | ProfitSEM"
  description="How a personal injury law firm achieved 13,333% ROI using hyper-local Google Ads targeting and conversion rate optimization."
>
  <Section background="white" spacing="lg">
    <Container size="lg">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <nav class="mb-8">
          <ol class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
            <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-blue-600">Home</a></li>
            <li>/</li>
            <li><a href="/case-studies" class="hover:text-blue-600">Case Studies</a></li>
            <li>/</li>
            <li class="text-gray-900">Law Firm Local Ads</li>
          </ol>
        </nav>

        <Badge variant="success" size="md" className="mb-6">Legal / Local Services</Badge>
        <Heading as="h1" size="5xl" className="mb-6">
          How a Law Firm Turned $18K into $2.4M in Signed Cases
        </Heading>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8">
          A personal injury law firm in Chicago was wasting money on broad keywords. We went hyper-local and ultra-targeted. ROI: 13,333%.
        </p>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mb-12">
          <Card className="text-center p-6">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-emerald-600 mb-2">13,333%</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">ROI</div>
          </Card>
          <Card className="text-center p-6">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-2">$2.4M</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Case Value</div>
          </Card>
          <Card className="text-center p-6">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-purple-600 mb-2">127</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Signed Cases</div>
          </Card>
          <Card className="text-center p-6">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-orange-600 mb-2">$142</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Cost Per Lead</div>
          </Card>
        </div>

        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
          <Heading as="h2" size="3xl" className="mb-4">
            The Client
          </Heading>

          <p>
            <strong>Industry:</strong> Personal Injury Law<br />
            <strong>Location:</strong> Chicago, IL<br />
            <strong>Previous Ad Spend:</strong> $22K/month<br />
            <strong>Problem:</strong> Too many unqualified leads, low case acceptance rate
          </p>

          <Heading as="h2" size="3xl" className="mb-4 mt-12">
            The Problem
          </Heading>

          <p>
            When this law firm came to us, they were spending $22,000/month on Google Ads with minimal returns:
          </p>

          <div class="bg-red-50 border-l-4 border-red-500 p-6 my-6">
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li><strong>Ad Spend:</strong> $22,000/month</li>
              <li><strong>Leads:</strong> 380/month</li>
              <li><strong>Cost Per Lead:</strong> $58</li>
              <li><strong>Cases Signed:</strong> 12/month</li>
              <li><strong>Case Acceptance Rate:</strong> 3.2%</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <p>
            The issues were clear:
          </p>

          <ul>
            <li>Targeting too broad (entire Chicago metro area + suburbs)</li>
            <li>Keywords too general ("lawyer", "attorney")</li>
            <li>Landing pages not conversion-optimized</li>
            <li>No call tracking or attribution</li>
            <li>Form leads mixed with phone calls (couldn't tell which converted better)</li>
          </ul>

          <Heading as="h2" size="3xl" className="mb-4 mt-12">
            The AI Training Approach
          </Heading>

          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
            For local services, Google's AI needed to learn which geographic areas and keywords drove signed cases, not just phone calls. Here's how we trained it:
          </p>

          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex gap-4 p-4 bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-200 rounded-lg">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-emerald-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">
                  1
                </div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-emerald-900 mb-1">Week 1-2: Connect The Dots</p>
                <p class="text-emerald-800 text-sm mb-2">Google needed to learn from signed cases, not just phone calls.</p>
                <ul class="text-emerald-700 text-sm space-y-1 list-disc list-inside">
                  <li>Integrated CallRail to track which keywords drove calls → consultations → signed cases</li>
                  <li>Set up offline conversion import: Call → Case Acceptance → Contract Signed</li>
                  <li>Discovered "car accident lawyer" calls had 24% acceptance vs "attorney" at 8%</li>
                  <li>Identified $9K/month wasted on 50-mile radius targeting (low conversion areas)</li>
                  <li>Blocked generic keywords immediately (saved $6K/month)</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex gap-4 p-4 bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-200 rounded-lg">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-emerald-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">
                  2
                </div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-emerald-900 mb-1">Week 3-6: Build Foundation & Let AI Learn</p>
                <p class="text-emerald-800 text-sm mb-2">Focused AI on high-value areas and intent-specific searches.</p>
                <ul class="text-emerald-700 text-sm space-y-1 list-disc list-inside">
                  <li>Tightened geo-targeting to 15-minute drive radius (high-accident corridors only)</li>
                  <li>Shifted to case-specific keywords ("car accident lawyer chicago" vs "lawyer")</li>
                  <li>Built call-first landing pages (78% calls vs forms—higher acceptance rate)</li>
                  <li>Let AI learn geographic and keyword patterns without daily changes</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex gap-4 p-4 bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-200 rounded-lg">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-emerald-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">
                  3
                </div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-emerald-900 mb-1">Week 7-12: Smart Bidding & Scaling</p>
                <p class="text-emerald-800 text-sm mb-2">AI automatically bid higher in high-acceptance areas and on case-specific keywords.</p>
                <ul class="text-emerald-700 text-sm space-y-1 list-disc list-inside">
                  <li>Activated target CPA smart bidding trained on signed cases (not calls)</li>
                  <li>Google identified high-traffic corridors converted 3x better than suburbs</li>
                  <li>AI automatically increased bids on "car accident" vs "personal injury" terms</li>
                  <li>Case acceptance rate stabilized at 18.6% (vs 3.2% before)—predictable pipeline</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-6 bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-500 rounded-r-lg p-4">
            <p class="text-sm text-blue-900">
              <strong>Why this worked:</strong> Google's AI learned that someone searching "car accident lawyer chicago" from a high-traffic corridor neighborhood was 8x more likely to sign a case than someone in the suburbs searching "attorney near me." Once trained on actual signed cases (via CallRail), it automatically optimized for high-value leads instead of cheap, unqualified calls.
            </p>
          </div>

          <Heading as="h2" size="3xl" className="mb-4 mt-12">
            The Results
          </Heading>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 my-8">
            <div>
              <Heading as="h3" size="xl" className="mb-4">
                Before
              </Heading>
              <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg space-y-3">
                <div>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Ad Spend</p>
                  <p class="text-2xl font-bold">$22,000/mo</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Leads</p>
                  <p class="text-2xl font-bold">380</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Cost Per Lead</p>
                  <p class="text-2xl font-bold">$58</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Cases Signed</p>
                  <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-600">12</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Avg Case Value</p>
                  <p class="text-2xl font-bold">$18,500</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Monthly Revenue</p>
                  <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-600">$222K</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div>
              <Heading as="h3" size="xl" className="mb-4">
                After (Month 6)
              </Heading>
              <div class="bg-emerald-50 p-6 rounded-lg space-y-3 border-2 border-emerald-500">
                <div>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Ad Spend</p>
                  <p class="text-2xl font-bold">$18,000/mo</p>
                  <p class="text-xs text-emerald-600">(-18% spend)</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Leads</p>
                  <p class="text-2xl font-bold">126</p>
                  <p class="text-xs text-emerald-600">(but 10x more qualified)</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Cost Per Lead</p>
                  <p class="text-2xl font-bold">$142</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Cases Signed</p>
                  <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-emerald-600">127</p>
                  <p class="text-xs text-emerald-600">(+958%)</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Avg Case Value</p>
                  <p class="text-2xl font-bold">$19,200</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Monthly Revenue</p>
                  <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-emerald-600">$2.4M</p>
                  <p class="text-xs text-emerald-600">(+982%)</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-emerald-50 border-2 border-emerald-500 rounded-lg p-8 my-8 text-center">
            <p class="text-6xl font-bold text-emerald-600 mb-4">13,333%</p>
            <p class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">ROI</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              Spent $18,000 | Generated $2,400,000 in case value
            </p>
          </div>

          <Heading as="h2" size="3xl" className="mb-4 mt-12">
            Key Lessons
          </Heading>

          <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-500 p-6 my-6">
            <p class="font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-3">What made this work:</p>
            <ol class="space-y-2 text-blue-800">
              <li><strong>1. Track the right conversion event.</strong> Google's AI optimized for signed cases (via CallRail), not cheap phone calls.</li>
              <li><strong>2. Geographic data is conversion data.</strong> AI learned which neighborhoods had 3x higher case acceptance rates.</li>
              <li><strong>3. Quality data enables smart bidding.</strong> Once AI knew what a signed case looked like, it optimized automatically.</li>
              <li><strong>4. Strategic patience works for local too.</strong> Let AI learn geographic and keyword patterns instead of changing bids daily.</li>
            </ol>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 my-12">
            <div class="flex gap-1 mb-6">
              {[1,2,3,4,5].map(() => (
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-yellow-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z" />
                </svg>
              ))}
            </div>

            <blockquote class="text-xl text-gray-900 mb-6 italic">
              "ProfitSEM didn't just improve our ads—they transformed our entire practice. We went from struggling to keep the lights on to having more cases than we can handle. Best decision we ever made."
            </blockquote>

            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold">
                DK
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold">David Kim, Esq.</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Managing Partner, Chicago Personal Injury Law</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-blue-700 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 text-white text-center shadow-xl my-12">
            <Heading as="h2" size="3xl" className="mb-4 text-white">
              Run a Professional Services Firm?
            </Heading>
            <p class="text-xl text-blue-100 mb-8">
              Get a free Google Ads audit tailored to local service businesses.
            </p>
            <Button variant="secondary" size="lg" href="/free-analysis">
              Get Free Audit
            </Button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </Section>
</BaseLayout>
